{"id":27,"parent_id":7,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":27,"title":"1 Nephi 20","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Ne.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 20"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lord reveals His purposes to Israel—Israel has been chosen in the furnace of affliction and is to go forth from Babylon—Compare",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/48"},"Isaiah 48"],". About 588–570",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.1","order":"05.12.020.2505"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Hearken"],"and hear this, O house of Jacob, who are called by the name of Israel, and are come forth out of the waters of Judah, or out of the waters of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"baptism"],", who",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"swear"],"by the name of the Lord, and make mention of the God of Israel, yet they swear",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"not"],"in truth nor in righteousness."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.2","order":"05.12.020.2506"},["b","2"],"Nevertheless, they call themselves of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"holy city"],", but they do",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"not"],"stay themselves upon the God of Israel, who is the Lord of Hosts; yea, the Lord of Hosts is his name."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.3","order":"05.12.020.2507"},["b","3"],"Behold, I have declared the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"former"],"things from the beginning; and they went forth out of my mouth, and I showed them. I did show them suddenly."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.4","order":"05.12.020.2508"},["b","4"],"And I did it because I knew that thou art obstinate, and thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"neck"],"is an iron sinew, and thy brow brass;"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.5","order":"05.12.020.2509"},["b","5"],"And I have even from the beginning declared to thee; before it came to pass I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"showed"],"them thee; and I showed them for fear lest thou shouldst say—Mine idol hath done them, and my graven image, and my molten image hath commanded them."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.6","order":"05.12.020.2510"},["b","6"],"Thou hast seen and heard all this; and will ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"not declare"],"them? And that I have showed thee new things from this time, even hidden things, and thou didst not know them."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.7","order":"05.12.020.2511"},["b","7"],"They are created now, and not from the beginning, even before the day when thou heardest them not they were declared unto thee, lest thou shouldst say—Behold I knew them."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.8","order":"05.12.020.2512"},["b","8"],"Yea, and thou heardest not; yea, thou knewest not; yea, from that time thine ear was not opened; for I knew that thou wouldst deal very treacherously, and wast called a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"transgressor"],"from the womb."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.9","order":"05.12.020.2513"},["b","9"],"Nevertheless, for my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"name’s"],"sake will I defer mine anger, and for my praise will I refrain from thee, that I cut thee not off."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.10","order":"05.12.020.2514"},["b","10"],"For, behold, I have refined thee, I have chosen thee in the furnace of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"affliction"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.11","order":"05.12.020.2515"},["b","11"],"For mine own sake, yea, for mine own sake will I do this, for I will not suffer my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"name"],"to be polluted, and I will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"not give"],"my glory unto another."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.12","order":"05.12.020.2516"},["b","12"],"Hearken unto me, O Jacob, and Israel my called, for I am he; I am the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"first"],", and I am also the last."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.13","order":"05.12.020.2517"},["b","13"],"Mine hand hath also",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"laid"],"the foundation of the earth, and my right hand hath spanned the heavens. I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"call"],"unto them and they stand up together."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.14","order":"05.12.020.2518"},["b","14"],"All ye, assemble yourselves, and hear; who among them hath declared these things unto them? The Lord hath loved him; yea, and he will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"fulfil"],"his word which he hath declared by them; and he will do his pleasure on",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"Babylon"],", and his arm shall come upon the Chaldeans."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.15","order":"05.12.020.2519"},["b","15"],"Also, saith the Lord; I the Lord, yea, I have spoken; yea, I have called",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"him"],"to declare, I have brought him, and he shall make his way prosperous."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.16","order":"05.12.020.2520"},["b","16"],"Come ye near unto me; I have not spoken in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"secret"],"; from the beginning, from the time that it was declared have I spoken; and the Lord God, and his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"Spirit"],", hath sent me."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.17","order":"05.12.020.2521"},["b","17"],"And thus saith the Lord, thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"Redeemer"],", the Holy One of Israel; I have sent him, the Lord thy God who teacheth thee to profit, who",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"leadeth"],"thee by the way thou shouldst go, hath done it."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.18","order":"05.12.020.2522"},["b","18"],"O that thou hadst hearkened to my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"commandments"],"—then had thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"peace"],"been as a river, and thy righteousness as the waves of the sea."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.19","order":"05.12.020.2523"},["b","19"],"Thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"seed"],"also had been as the sand; the offspring of thy bowels like the gravel thereof; his name should not have been cut off nor destroyed from before me."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.20","order":"05.12.020.2524"},["b","20"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"Go"],"ye forth of Babylon, flee ye from the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"Chaldeans"],", with a voice of singing declare ye, tell this, utter to the end of the earth; say ye: The Lord hath redeemed his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"servant"],"Jacob."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.21","order":"05.12.020.2525"},["b","21"],"And they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"thirsted"],"not; he led them through the deserts; he caused the waters to flow out of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"rock"],"for them; he clave the rock also and the waters gushed out."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.22","order":"05.12.020.2526"},["b","22"],"And notwithstanding he hath done all this, and greater also, there is no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"peace"],", saith the Lord, unto the wicked."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.1a","order":"05.12.020.2527"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/48.1.1-22"},"Isa. 48:1 (1–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.1b","order":"05.12.020.2529"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/baptism"},"TG Baptism"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conversion"},"Conversion"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.1c","order":"05.12.020.2531"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/6.13"},"Deut. 6:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.1d","order":"05.12.020.2533"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.2"},"Jer. 4:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.2"},"5:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.2a","order":"05.12.020.2535"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/52.1"},"Isa. 52:1"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jerusalem"},"TG Jerusalem"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.2b","order":"05.12.020.2537"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hypocrisy"},"TG Hypocrisy"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-rejection-of"},"Prophets, Rejection of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.3a","order":"05.12.020.2539"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/42.9"},"Isa. 42:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/46.10.9-10"},"46:10 (9–10)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-foreknowledge-of"},"TG God, Foreknowledge of"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.4a","order":"05.12.020.2541"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stiffnecked"},"TG Stiffnecked"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.5a","order":"05.12.020.2543"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-omniscience-of"},"TG God, Omniscience of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idolatry"},"Idolatry"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.6a","order":"05.12.020.2545"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.16"},"1 Cor. 9:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.8a","order":"05.12.020.2547"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/58.3"},"Ps. 58:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.9a","order":"05.12.020.2549"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scripture